description: Welcome to 232 Old Colony, with this upper corner unit offering 2 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and a private office. This luxury South Boston contemporary condo boasts high-end features throughout including an open-concept layout with high ceilings, gorgeous hardwood floors, floor-to-ceiling windows offering abundant natural light, recessed lighting, elegantly appointed bathroom with Carrara marble shower. The unit is southeast facing, allowing for ample natural light throughout the day and sweeping views. The gourmet kitchen boasts a large center island, Jenn Air stainless appliances,custom cabinetry and premium quartz countertops. Modern amenities include custom blinds, large custom-fitted closets, in-unit washer/dryer &built-in Sonos system creating an inviting space for relaxation or entertaining. The unit also comes with a premier deeded garage parking spot with ample room for extra storage. Experience sophistication and urban elegance at its best!
